# CSP Playground agent context

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for full project guidance.

## Quick reference

- **Yarn only** for dependencies; `yarn.lock` is canonical.
- **TSDoc** for TypeScript documentation in `src/`, `server/`, `functions/`.
- **Tests:** `yarn test` · **Build:** `yarn build`
- **Dependency updates:** pin exact versions, then run `yarn verify:deps` **once** after all updates — see `.cursor/rules/dependency-pinning.mdc`.
- **Cloudflare Pages v3:** Node `22.16.0` via `.nvmrc`; Yarn `1.22.22` via `YARN_VERSION` build env var (v3 defaults to Yarn 4) — see `.cursor/rules/cloudflare-pages-v3.mdc`.
- **Before finishing:** fix all test errors and lint warnings; update `AGENTS.md` when needed — see `.cursor/rules/finish-quality-gate.mdc`.

## Scope discipline

- Minimize diffs; match existing patterns in surrounding code.
- Do not commit unless the user explicitly requests it.
